Sarah Laine https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sarah_Laine 0 Sarah Laine (born Serah D'Laine on October 23, 1982 in Santa Barbara, California) is an American actress. She is best known for her role as Sarah Webber in General Hospital. She has played in several films as well, including starring in Wild Things: Diamonds in the Rough and Mermaids.
